title: Frommer's Belize (5th Edition) by Ali Wunderman (.epub)
description:
Frommer's Belize (Complete Guides), 5th Edition by Ali Wunderman

Requirements: .ePUB reader

Overview: Belize is a rising star. With all of the natural allure of Costa Rica, it adds to the mix towering ancient pyramids, superb scuba diving and snorkeling (along the world’s second-longest coral reef system), and a culture that’s warm and welcoming. Author Ali Wunderman has been covering the country for years and uses her expertise to help you craft the vacation of your dreams.

Genre: Non-Fiction > General
